<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA57">
<l>nāmpeṟṟa naṉmaiyu nāmaṅkai naṉṉeñcat</l>
<l>tōmpi yiruntemmai yōtuvittu – vēmpiṉ</l>
<l>poruṇīrmai yāyiṉum poṉṉāḻi pāṭeṉ</l>
<l>ṟaruṇīrmai tanta varuḷ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All the goodness we obtain is by the grace of the tongue Lady,</l>
<l>who gives the essence of grace by keeping [us] protected in [her] good heart,</l>
<l>making us recite, saying ‘even if the essence of [earthly] riches</l>
<l>is like a Neem fruit, sing of the golden discus.’</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
